  "title": "10 ft Lorry Driver",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<p>1. Be responsible for the company’s daily dispatching of vehicles that are idle, stacked and out of the required areas to ensure the timeliness and effectiveness of dispatching. Dispatch vehicles from inefficient areas to efficient ones.</p>\n<p>2. Mark and recycle the defective vehicles in required areas everyday, and then put them into the operation area after repairing them.</p>\n<p>3. Be responsible for the daily dispatch, timely cleaning and maintenance of vehicles.</p>\n<p>4. If vehicles are not neatly placed on the road, you need help to tidy them up in a timely manner.</p>\n<p>5. During the dispatching process, carry out loading and unloading operations strictly according to requirements and provide photos as feedback.</p>\n<p>6. Actively cooperate with other posts to assist in handling abnormal vehicles.</p>\n<p>Job Qualifications:</p>\n<p>1. Be experienced in driving and having a license.</p>\n<p>2. Have good communication skills. Be righteous, responsible and hard-working.</p>\n<p>3. Good physical condition.</p>\n<p>1. Be experienced in using smartphones.</p>\n<p>2. People who have simple maintenance experience skills are preferred.</p>",
