    "description": "<p>Founded in 2016, Hello Inc. (formerly known as Hellobike) is a leading mobility platform in China specialized in providing easy, efficient, universal and safe access to rides on demand. The comprehensive mobility platform offers diversified ride options covering two-wheelers including shared bikes, e-bikes, e-scooters and battery swap, as well as four-wheelers including Hello Pool, Hello Aggregated car-hailing and Hello Hailing, and has accumulated more than 400 million users.</p>\n<p>By the end of October 2020 Hello’s shared bike service had helped riders in 460 cities across China travel a total of 24 billion kilometers; Its shared e-bikes are available in nearly 400 cities and have completed a total distance of 8 billion kilometers.</p>",
